name: Black Rose Plugs 1 1/2 1 3/8 Inch 35mm 38mm
description:
Beautiful rose plugs!!!! I love these soooo much I just may have to stretch up to be able to wear a pair! They would be perfect for a wedding or fancy night out. Heck they can even be dressed down and worn everyday!

Made with stainless steel double flare tunnels (overall width is 10mm). Price is for a pair.

Sizes avaliable
1 3/8" (35mm)
1 1/2" (38mm)

*****During checkout please indicate what size and color you would like for the reverse side.
